IndentStyles(style=k&r) \</br><br />
NewLines(before=if:switch:T_CLASS,after=function) \</br><br />
Pear(add_header=apache) \</br><br />
ArrayNested() \</br><br />
Lowercase()\</br><br />
-f myfile.php</br></p>
